Indiana Michigan Power


	Indiana Michigan Power provides Internet access
        to its state jurisdictional tariff documents for the convenience of its customers.
        Indiana Michigan Power makes no warranty that a
        particular tariff/schedule chosen by a customer is available to or suitable for
        that customer. Customers are encouraged to contact
        Indiana Michigan Power directly to ensure the applicability
        of a desired tariff/schedule for their service requirements.







