Frequently Asked Questions
Questions about Indiana Michigan Power? Maybe we can help.


Does Indiana Michigan Power offer online bill pay?
Indiana Michigan Power can be paid online through doxo. Click here to make a payment to Indiana Michigan Power to make a payment. Indiana Michigan Power can also be paid online at their website.  Click here to make a payment to Indiana Michigan Power for Indiana Michigan Power bill pay, or visit the Indiana Michigan Power website at www.indianamichiganpower.com


How can I sign into my Indiana Michigan Power account online?
You can login to your Indiana Michigan Power account online on their site at: www.indianamichiganpower.com.


I'm not able to login to my online Indiana Michigan Power account.  Where can I get help?
The support team for Indiana Michigan Power can assist with your account access questions.  View their contact information here: www.indianamichiganpower.com.


Can I access my account or pay Indiana Michigan Power from my phone or tablet?
Indiana Michigan Power does not offer their customers a mobile app for iOS or Android.  You can use the doxo My Account Manager app to keep your account info, notes, documents, and contact information for Indiana Michigan Power.  Download and install doxo My Account Manager for iPhone or doxo My Account Manager for Android now.


How do I contact Indiana Michigan Power if I have a question about my account or bill?
Indiana Michigan Power offers customer support via their website at www.indianamichiganpower.com. You can also contact Indiana Michigan Power via phone at (800) 311-4634.


Does Indiana Michigan Power go by another name?
No, the primary name is "Indiana Michigan Power".


Can I pay Indiana Michigan Power with a debit card?
Yes, you can pay Indiana Michigan Power with your Discover, MasterCard or Visa Debit Card. Indiana Michigan Power is also payable via debit card at their website.


Can I pay Indiana Michigan Power with a credit card?
Yes, you can pay Indiana Michigan Power with your Discover, MasterCard or Visa Credit Card. Indiana Michigan Power is also payable via credit card at their website.


 




